rows.label: qst201415_0010
rows.name:
Hey. Looks like the sun should be
up before long. What time is it?

rows.label: qst201415_0020
rows.name:
Uh... It's seven o'clock. I
guess the contest is over.

rows.label: qst201415_0030
rows.name:
So it is...but we don't really
have a clear winner yet...

rows.label: qst201415_0050
rows.name:
Zakuro... I'm starting to
get the measure of you now.

rows.label: qst201415_0060
rows.name:
I hate to admit it...but you do
have more Girl Power than me.

rows.label: qst201415_0070
rows.name: Well, that's really big of you, Hikari.

rows.label: qst201415_0080
rows.name:
You're my only rival when it comes
to Girl Power. I salute you.

rows.label: qst201415_0110
rows.name: Ah, well, I'm pooped. But it was fun.

rows.label: qst201415_0120
rows.name:
Sure was! I had a great time. Maybe
we should do it again sometime?

rows.label: qst201415_0160
rows.name:
So...how come you're
all gathered together?

rows.label: qst201415_0170
rows.name:
Well now. Your little contest
might be over, girls...

rows.label: qst201415_0180
rows.name: But there's one more judgment to make.

rows.label: qst201415_0190
rows.name:
It's about all your
reckless gallivanting!

rows.label: qst201415_0200
rows.name:
Time for a little court
martial, I think.

rows.label: qst201415_0230
rows.name:
Didn't we help you discover
YOUR inner Girl Power, too?

rows.label: qst201415_0300
rows.name:
You can't go around
doing stuff like that.

rows.label: qst201415_0320
rows.name:
You should think about all
the hassle you've caused us.

rows.label: qst201415_0380
rows.name:
In that case... The epic contest
concludes without a victor.

rows.label: qst201415_0390
rows.name:
That means two losers...and
two forfeits.

rows.label: qst201415_0450
rows.name:
Why does this stuff keep
happening to me...?

rows.label: qst201415_0460
rows.name:
Hikari, don't complain. You talked
the talk, now dance the dance.
